data.name: lbTrustProxyHost.ToolTip
data.value: # List of IP addresses or subnets that should be trusted as a reverse proxy. # Multiple entries can be listed separated by commas. # If left empty, headers will be accepted from any IP address (not recommended!).

data.name: cbTrustProxy.ToolTip
data.value: # Allow determination of client IP address based on "X-Forwarded-For" header. # This must be enabled if a reverse proxy is used. It is also necessary to specify the reverse # proxy IP address in parameter TRUST PROXY HOSTS, otherwise data spoofing is possible.
